    "Ethics statement for the multisensebadminton dataset.",
    "The development of the MultiSenseBadminton dataset received ethical clearance from the Institutional Review Board (IRB) at the Gwangju Institute of Science and Technology 75.",
    "This project was approved under the protocol code 20220628-HR-67-20-04 on July 21, 2022.",
    "Upon arrival at the data collection site, participants were presented with consent forms.",
